{"tid":1118432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半夜「被壓床」不能呼吸　他偷設監視器…起床見驚人一幕","createTime":"2019-04-21T12:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T12:46:21.000Z","uid":32511,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa130c03d215ab2db0e8d833a5b6ca856de2395","tid":1118432,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:02:55.000Z","msg":"一名男網友發文，透露有一名「苦主」每晚睡覺都呼吸不順，好像「被壓」，於是決定架設攝影機，看看在他睡覺時究竟發生了什麼事。沒想到影片曝光後，他竟發現驚人的一幕，而網友看到後也狂喊：「這怨念也太深！」<br />\n<br />\n泰國一名貓奴在「貓情人俱樂部」臉書社團分享了家中愛貓的逗趣行徑，只見當天凌晨一點多，喵皇坐在枕頭旁邊看著熟睡的奴才，不時用小手輕撥臉頰，之後又偷偷爬上床，一下趴在奴才的大腿，一下又跑到胸口，接著更用雙手環抱奴才的脖子，看似「主僕情深」，舒服的靠在他的臉上睡著。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/21/1886562-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2F1886562-XXL.jpg&h=0ae6afa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/21/1886560-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2F1886560-XXL.jpg&h=e6dd313c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過喵皇似乎沒發現主人都快喘不過氣，軟趴趴的身軀直接堵住他的口鼻，也讓這幾張照片被網友瘋傳到各大臉書社團。其中一名網友就將文章轉貼到「爆笑公社」，搞笑表示：「這位苦主說，他每天起床後呼吸很不順暢，所以暗中架設攝影機拍攝睡眠狀況，结果拍到很驚人的畫面。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/21/1886564-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2F1886564-XXL.jpg&h=e5db0a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/21/1886561-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F21%2F1886561-XXL.jpg&h=7d787d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而網友看到照片後也笑說「終於解開疑似鬼壓床的謎題啦」、「怨念是多深，要趁你睡著報復一下」、「喵皇終於受不了這個奴才的打呼，決定趁月黑風高把他幹掉了」，更有人替這組照片命名「令人窒息的愛」。而PO文曝光短短幾個小時，就吸引了超過3萬網友按讚、1800多人留言、2600多次分享。"},{"pid":"80e19194fd72a7537448e879008551a12d213c84","tid":1118432,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"身在福中不知福"},{"pid":"dbccb022c2f459a8463f91048d973275db8db3e3","tid":1118432,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好感動"},{"pid":"b68d522b8392f2425118a74b5eea9eb320bbb4a9","tid":1118432,"uid":54930,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/theoatmeal-img/comics/cat_kill/header.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Ftheoatmeal-img%2Fcomics%2Fcat_kill%2Fheader.png&h=c2e871d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a36896dc0d01658741e2e6c3b160ca4ead815f8f","tid":1118432,"uid":155815,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"謀殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貓星人終於要反抗人類"},{"pid":"1e6f60e3802bc9dbdaff325f0fa87b62dcc29190","tid":1118432,"uid":65384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"想焗死個貓奴好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e7a2caa136cc8a19cd30cbbd2501f33f6f0599","tid":1118432,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af25ea85791f6e48dc0a26f13e44b313254b6fb","tid":1118432,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"人類終於揾到證據啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96fa7680